Navneet Education Ltdhas informed BSE that the meeting of the Board of Directors of the Company is scheduled on 10/11/2025 inter alia to consider and approve 
1. consider approve and take on record the Standalone and Consolidated Unaudited Financial Results of the Company for the quarter and half year ended 30th September 2025;

2. consider declaration of interim dividend if any for the Financial Year 2025-26 and to fix the record date for the same.
